      • Section

        public Section(boolean dumpFormat,
       java.lang.String course,
       java.lang.String section,
       int day,
       java.util.Date start,
       java.util.Date end,
       java.lang.String instructor,
       java.lang.String venue,
       int size)
        Specific constructor to allow day to be represented as a String E.g. "Monday" instead of 1. Mainly used by the Dump Tables.
        Parameters:
        dumpFormat - - set to true if you want dumpFormat to be displayed.
        course - Course Code
        section - Each course has multiple sections (S1,S2 etc). The section number is a number less than 100.
        day - The day of week
        start - The start time of the class
        end - The end time of the class
        instructor - The instructor of the class
        venue - The venue where the class is going to be conducted
        size - The class size
